These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, disaster
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, designer
1. the journalist is on the far left##1
2. the designer is not the person watching disaster movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | disaster   | sports  |
| Sport   | journalist | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, italian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, musical
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is not the italian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | argentine | italian      |
| Pet    | disaster  | musical |

 #################################

 
