.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, october
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher
1. the person who's birthday is in october is not the vegafina-smoker##6
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | february  | october |
| Pet    | vegafina | swisher    |

